text: Coat of Arms of Oudkarspel Oudkarspel is a village in the Dutch province of North Holland. It is located in the municipality of Langedijk, north of the town of Noord-Scharwoude. Oudkarspel was a separate municipality until 1941, when the new municipality of Langedijk was created. ==References== ==External links== * Map of the former municipality, around 1868.
